Coke studio coming up with such a soulful rendition was unexpected!

I'm supposed to be sleeping early tonight!
Don't think that's possible at the moment!
Cannot get enough of this!

The lyrics, the kaalaam that is...wrenches so much out of the soul and into the night air that surrounds you!
Its *sigh* amazing!

"Anaginat sadiyon ke taariq bahimanaa talism
The dark magic of uncountable dark years "
